snippet.title: Starship Simulator - Development Video #1
snippet.description:
Our first ever dev video for Starship Simulator, which I hope will be the start of regular video updates. Please let us know your thoughts in the comments, and if you like what you see we'd be incredibly grateful for your support in bringing this game to life.

Chat in our community on Discord: https://discord.gg/eDSQvpgdUX​

https://www.paypal.me/StarshipSimulator​
https://www.patreon.com/starshipsimul...​

Follow us on 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Starship_sim​
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Starshipgame
